item.title: Strange compile problem
item.dc:creator: @dogzound5 dogzound5@gmail.com
item.description:
@dogzound5 wrote:

See this jdk1.6.0_07??

ON your compiler you need to set that to the version of Java you have.

Go to Program Files/java/jdk

you will see your version in the path bar. Replace your version with the one already in your compiler.
